Subject: Re: [T2] bus stereos/speaker placement

If you pull your front kick panels, you will find a large space on each
side just medial to the door posts- I put 6x9 dual cone speakers in
these spaces, as I hate the imbalance of side mounted speakers.  I cut
my own panels out of thin plywood; they are stiffer than the paperboard
stock panels.

